@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_guiwld(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (tmp + 0.75)
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.cos(wp.abs(v2 + 0.60)))
    tmp = wp.sin(v2)
    v2 = (0.92 / (wp.cos(tmp + 0.76) + 0.69))
    v1 = (0.76 * ((v0 + 0.96 * v1 + 0.99) + 0.65))
    v0 = 0.88
    data[tid] = v0
